1
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:56,280
Water is really a good thing.

2
00:02:57,880 --> 00:02:58,880
Sister Gesang.

3
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:00,840
You were so badly injured.

4
00:03:01,040 --> 00:03:03,640
Drinking some water will make you feel better.

5
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:10,200
It doesn't work that fast.

6
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:12,080
It just restored a little bit of my strength.

7
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:14,000
Let's hurry to Brother Qingxuan's side.

8
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:16,079
We don't know the situation there yet.

9
00:03:16,079 --> 00:03:16,840
Okay.

10
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:57,240
Golden blade shines,

11
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:58,840
breaking through all obstacles.

12
00:03:58,840 --> 00:04:00,280
Embracing the origin and returning to the center,

13
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:01,610
heaven and earth shake.

14
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,200
Sister,

15
00:04:43,760 --> 00:04:46,159
when can we ascend to become immortals?

16
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:48,140
Heaven must be really fun.

17
00:04:53,880 --> 00:04:55,810
As long as we sisters are together,

18
00:04:55,880 --> 00:04:58,280
what does it matter if we become immortals?

19
00:05:03,400 --> 00:05:05,260
Then you must always stay with me.

20
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:10,900
It's a promise.

21
00:05:38,280 --> 00:05:39,080
Sister.

22
00:05:42,080 --> 00:05:43,140
Wait for my return.

23
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,640
Sister.

24
00:06:09,440 --> 00:06:10,160
My sister.

25
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:13,160
There is a Sanshan Liu in heaven.

26
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:15,480
There,

27
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:18,360
lives a High God.

28
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:40,400
Sister,

29
00:06:41,320 --> 00:06:42,650
what are you looking at?

30
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:02,640
Come back earlier this time.

31
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:05,760
Wait for me.

32
00:08:28,840 --> 00:08:29,640
You lied to me.

33
00:08:33,280 --> 00:08:34,440
You lied to me.

34
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:37,559
You lied to me.

35
00:09:18,520 --> 00:09:19,680
I never expected

36
00:09:20,560 --> 00:09:21,490
that this matter

37
00:09:22,680 --> 00:09:24,340
would drag you into the abyss.

38
00:09:26,400 --> 00:09:27,200
What a pity.

39
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:30,000
Since you have attained the right path

40
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:31,660
and become a Golden Immortal,

41
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:34,920
why did you still disturb her peace?

42
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:39,720
My sister and I could have lived carefree in the Three Realms.

43
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:45,040
My sister promised me herself

44
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:47,520
to guard the Hanmei Dock with me

45
00:09:48,920 --> 00:09:51,250
and watch all the snow in the mortal world.

46
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:54,680
But you,

47
00:09:56,920 --> 00:09:58,720
you ruined her cultivation path

48
00:09:59,280 --> 00:10:00,680
and our promise.

49
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:05,720
I will make you pay with your life.

50
00:10:06,680 --> 00:10:07,810
If I didn't help her,

51
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:11,920
she would have been destroyed by the heavenly lightning.

52
00:10:12,640 --> 00:10:13,440
What?

53
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:16,610
The heavenly law is strict.

54
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:19,080
How could we arbitrarily change it?

55
00:10:19,680 --> 00:10:20,320
That day,

56
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:23,450
she would rather lose all her cultivation

57
00:10:23,680 --> 00:10:25,520
than follow the heavenly rules.

58
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:32,090
If I didn't agree to help her keep that thread of longing,

59
00:10:32,880 --> 00:10:35,080
the nine-fold lightning would strike,

60
00:10:35,680 --> 00:10:37,940
and her body and soul would be destroyed.

61
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:40,580
This thread of longing

62
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,000
not only kept her alive

63
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,000
but

64
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:45,960
also caused her to

65
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:48,660
fall into a love tribulation.

66
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:52,100
This action breaks the rules.

67
00:10:52,520 --> 00:10:53,720
How could I not know?

68
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:57,920
But after a thousand years of hard cultivation

69
00:10:57,920 --> 00:10:59,720
to encounter immortal destiny,

70
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:02,320
if it fails at the last step

71
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:04,720
and her body and soul are destroyed,

72
00:11:04,880 --> 00:11:05,940
what's the point of

73
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:08,920
this righteous path?

74
00:11:09,680 --> 00:11:10,600
So,

75
00:11:12,520 --> 00:11:14,580
you were banished to the mortal realm

76
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:18,040
all because of my sister?

77
00:11:19,520 --> 00:11:22,720
Although my descent to the mortal realm started with her,

78
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:23,940
I was not banished.

79
00:11:25,640 --> 00:11:27,100
I came to this mortal world

80
00:11:27,680 --> 00:11:29,080
to do what I want

81
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:31,240
and meet who I want to see.

82
00:11:32,680 --> 00:11:33,840
But I didn't expect

83
00:11:36,040 --> 00:11:38,360
that she would also give up her immortal status

84
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:40,020
and come to this mortal world.

85
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:41,880
What?

86
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:45,610
My sister is also in this mortal world?

87
00:11:49,480 --> 00:11:50,210
Bai Jingqing

88
00:11:50,880 --> 00:11:53,340
volunteered to descend to the mortal realm.

89
00:11:54,800 --> 00:11:56,320
Why did she have to do this?

90
00:11:58,680 --> 00:12:00,720
Since the High God descended to the mortal realm,

91
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:01,720
Bai Jingqing

92
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:04,850
felt that it was because of her thread of longing.

93
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:08,770
So she resolutely gave up her immortal status

94
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:10,740
and entered the mortal world.

95
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:14,840
Where is she now?

96
00:12:15,680 --> 00:12:16,520
Right now,

97
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,520
she is in Tushan.

98
00:12:19,640 --> 00:12:20,640
What?

99
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:22,200
Where is she?

100
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:28,540
Master, your immortal power has recovered.

101
00:12:34,040 --> 00:12:35,160
It is indeed him.

102
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:50,850
The Way of Heaven is unfair.

103
00:12:52,600 --> 00:12:55,000
Why does it toy with us sisters like this?

104
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:57,240
Sisters?

105
00:12:58,640 --> 00:12:59,640
Who?

106
00:12:59,640 --> 00:13:02,080
When has the Way of Heaven ever been partial?

107
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:03,280
Every drink and peck,

108
00:13:03,640 --> 00:13:04,640
are predestined.

109
00:13:06,280 --> 00:13:08,080
You are merely in this game,

110
00:13:08,880 --> 00:13:11,920
mistaking opportunities for calamities.

111
00:13:13,520 --> 00:13:14,120
High God.

112
00:13:14,880 --> 00:13:16,720
Although this demon has gone astray,

113
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:18,480
she has a thousand years of cultivation.

114
00:13:18,480 --> 00:13:20,880
The Li Sword came down to the mortal realm without permission.

115
00:13:20,880 --> 00:13:23,080
The Heavenly Venerable is looking for a sword attendant.

116
00:13:23,080 --> 00:13:25,040
If she is allowed to make up for her mistakes

117
00:13:25,040 --> 00:13:27,040
by guarding this blade for ten thousand years,

118
00:13:27,040 --> 00:13:28,480
would it be possible?

119
00:13:30,680 --> 00:13:31,480
If so,

120
00:13:33,280 --> 00:13:35,080
it would be a win-win solution.

121
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:41,320
Are you willing to cultivate with me

122
00:13:42,080 --> 00:13:43,680
to make up for your mistakes?

123
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:45,520
You want to take me in?

124
00:13:46,880 --> 00:13:47,920
Don't think everyone wants to

125
00:13:47,920 --> 00:13:50,120
have anything to do with you immortals.

126
00:15:01,600 --> 00:15:01,760
Hai Hui.

127
00:15:01,760 --> 00:15:02,280
Jie Qianghai.
